==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cinchonism
<hw>Cin"cho*nism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Cinchona</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A condition produced by
the excessive or long-continued use of quinine, and marked by deafness,
roaring in the ears, vertigo, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cinchonize</ent>⟦br⟧
